    div(class="template-section m-a")
        section(class="template-content")
            h5 Read on the following topics and express your opinion by recording it. 
            .row.mt50
                
                .col.xs12.sm6
                    p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] The use of computers and computer systems in schools, how do you think this has changed education?
                    .row.align-items-center.flex.ta-c.mt30
                        .col.xs6.md4.ta-r
                            img(class="u-responsive-img w100" src="unit_1/module_3/assets/images/col_10_1.png", alt="myColombia")
                        .col.xs6.md8
                            div(class="row c-ngRecorder" ng-audio-recorder id="mainAudio_a" time-limit='120' audio-model="audio_1" on-playback-start="guardarRecord('unt1_mod3_mycol1',1)"): +ngRecorder
                .col.xs12.sm6
                    p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] Do you believe that corporal punishment should still be allowed in school? Give some reasons for and some reasons against corporal punishment and then a conclusion?
                    .row.align-items-center.flex.ta-c.mt30
                        .col.xs6.md4.ta-r
                            img(class="u-responsive-img w100" src="unit_1/module_3/assets/images/col_10_2.png", alt="myColombia")
                        .col.xs6.md8
                            div(class="row c-ngRecorder" ng-audio-recorder id="mainAudio_b" time-limit='120' audio-model="audio_2" on-playback-start="guardarRecord('unt1_mod3_mycol2',2)"): +ngRecorder
                
                .col.xs12.sm6
                    p #[strong.u-textColor_4 •] How important do you think school lunch is to a child’s education? Does it affect their learning? Is it the government’s responsibility or parents’ responsibility?
                    .row.align-items-center.flex.ta-c.mt30
                        .col.xs6.md4.ta-r
